E.Soukhovitskii and R. Capote
Nucl. Data Sheets 110 (2009) 3107-3214 (RIPL paper)
Lane consistent dispersive CC proton OMP for incident energies between 1 keV
and 200 MeV for Hf-W-Ta isotope. Recommended for Hf-178,180, Ta-181, all W.
Local Fermi energy used. See 610 for neutron OMP. Rigid rotor.
Ep = Ep - 1.33 Z/A**1/3, rc=1.0626, ac=0.64.
